features: DOUBLE LAYERS PROTECTION: This newly designed file folder uses different materials than other folder.Double Layered design, high quality Black Non-itchy Liquid Silicone Coated Fireproof Fiberglass which feels very comfortable to touch,this bag is FIRE and WATER RESISTANT.Fireproof file folders can fully protect your important documents, paper,birth certificate, passport.It will be an ideal great Chirstmas gift for your family or friends.

SIZE: 14.3" x 9.8" (Easily expand to 1.18inches),Weight:400g/14ounce,13 individual pockets. Fireproof file folder makes it suitable for daily filing and storing of documents(with Color Labels); perfect for both A4 size and letter size.

WIDE RANGE OF APPLICATIONS: Fireproof zipper added security and safe transport.It's very durable.Not only can you put your file folder at home, office, car,it's also a good decision to put it in the safe box. You can be 100% assured that your important information is in a safe place.

Original Intention:Accidents happen when we least expect, and there’s nothing more devastating than a fire that takes away valuable paperwork, personal information, pictures or achievements.That’s why we developed the fireproof document bag- Protect your financials, personal information,document notebook, that won’t let you down when emergency strikes.
CUSTOMER SERVICE: ENGPOW provide friendly after-sale service and no risk refund for our customers. If you have any issue,please contact us and we will try out best to solve your issue.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Feels durable & seemingly great quality!
reviews.reviewText: I hope I never have to see if this is actually fireproof *knocks on wood*, but the quality seems pretty great. I purchased 2 and able to fit a lot of paperwork in one from my time in the military (mostly paperwork from getting discharged) and paperwork in the other one for my family to include birth certs, important baby paperwork, etc. Fits perfectly in a backpack that I can grab for myself and my family in case of an emergency.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pay attention to the size, I thought it would have been smaller.
reviews.reviewText: Very nice, well made. Again, I thought it would have been smaller.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The only thing I didn't like is the bottom of the file inside there's a small space between the accordion fold where smaller things I have such as certain business cards fall through a bit and go into the next compartment/section/file. Otherwise papers fit perfectly and are kept very neat. The zipper is slightly larger than a normal zipper making it easier to open which I appreciate. Color and material is nice, definitely seems weather proof from current observations but have not tested for accuracy. Plenty of room and good amount of storage. Definitely like this folder apart from the small inconvenience of the bottom portion. I can understand if that part was left with a slight opening to allow more storage and use less material but I would have liked to keep business cards and small papers in as well without them mixing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for holding files
reviews.reviewText: I doubt this is fireproof, but it's a zippered file folder. It works great with no issues. I wouldn't expect this to protect against water or fire but it works fine for holding files.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soft but durable
reviews.reviewText: I took this with me to Europe to hold all my legal documents, receipts, tickets and souvenirs. It worked pretty good and the soft shell was helpful for when it packed my bags to full capacity. nothing got wet or damaged. It held these items for 6 months and i filled it completely. the organizer may be deformed a bit now, but it never tore and the zipper works perfect. this was exactly what i needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well built Document Holder
reviews.reviewText: Best Document holder I've had. Material is great and strong as are the 3 inside partitions. Zippers smooth as glass and perfect size for legal papers. Very satisfied with this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Love this & is easy to grab if there is a hurricane evacuation. Not cumbersome at all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Doesn’t have folders inside, they are only separators.
reviews.reviewText: This is pretty good quality and sturdy but I actually thought all the folders inside were actual folders not just connected pages with no bottom, so if you plan on putting small things like business cards or anything not large it will end up going to the bottom and leaving the area that you originally put it in. There are no bottoms to the folders. Just plastic sheets that separate everything. Just weird. Not what I wanted personally
The folder is perfect size for all my documents. Very durable and high quality, can fit lots of paper and thick documents, I love the tabs that I can be organized. I would highly recommend.
Excelente servicio llego antes de lo esperado, cumple su función aunque las orillas sí se queman... proporciona cuidado mayor al de un folder manila para documentos importantes.
I purchased this so I can get rid of most of my paperwork and only keep what I need. This will be very handy.

Perfect for what I need it for! I can't confirm if it fireproof, but it seems durable and the zipper glides well. The outer lining is a rubbery texture and unfortunately attracts lint/hair which is why i gave it 4 stars. Pictures were taken right after I took it out of its bag and as you can see, there's already lint attached to it.
I like how it looks, and the feel of it, I use it everyday.
